The,Mozilla,Permissions,API,makes,it,easier,for,users,to,determine,the,accessibility,of,APIs,The,API,allows,developers,to,build,applications,that,provide,consistent,options,for,querying,the,statuses,of,APIs,This,makes,it,possible,users,to,query,the,granting,or,denial,of,permissions,to,access,APIs,The,API,s,support,for,desktop,browsers,is,currently,restricted,to,Chrome,and,Firefox,Gecko,while,the,mobile,browsers,it,supports,include,Android,Webview,Firefox,Mobile,Gecko,and,Chrome,for,Android